The paper is focused on multiagent teamwork, which is a subfield of multiagent systems (cs.MA). The paper also discusses the use of decision-making models and algorithms, which are common topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also touches on game theory (cs.GT) and system theory (cs.SY) in its analysis of the optimality and complexity of teamwork. Finally, the paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms in developing coordination algorithms, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG).
